#: data/org.gnome.Taquin.gschema.xml:53
msgid ""
"The game offers to play with a board size from 3 to 5. The setting could be "
"set from 2 (good for testing) to 9, limited by the way files are selected."
msgstr ""
"The game offers to play with a board size from 3 to 5. The setting could be "
"set from 2 (good for testing) to 9, limited by the way files are selected."

