#: data/org.gnome.Taquin.metainfo.xml.in:7
msgid "GNOME Taquin"
msgstr "GNOME Taquin"

#: data/org.gnome.Taquin.metainfo.xml.in:10
msgid ""
"Taquin is a computer version of the 15-puzzle and other sliding puzzles."
msgstr ""
"Taquin は15 パズルを始めとするスライド式パズルゲームのコンピューターバージョ"
"ンです。"

#: data/org.gnome.Taquin.metainfo.xml.in:13
msgid ""
"The object of Taquin is to move tiles so that they reach their places, "
"either indicated with numbers, or with parts of a great image."
msgstr ""
"Taquin の目的は、数字で示された場所や、巨大な絵がうまく完成するような場所に"
"タイルを動かすことです。"

#: data/org.gnome.Taquin.metainfo.xml.in:21
msgid "A GNOME taquin game preview"
msgstr "GNOME taquin ゲームのプレビュー"

#: data/org.gnome.Taquin.metainfo.xml.in:37
msgid "The GNOME Project"
msgstr "The GNOME Project"

